results.cleanName: Legendary Decks II Collectors Set 1st Edition

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value:
Each Legendary Decks II Collector's Set contains:

- 43-card Deck based on Yugi and his "Exodia the Forbidden One", including the 3 playable versions of the Egyptian God cards.
- 43-card Deck based on Kaiba and his "Blue-Eyes White Dragon".
- 43-card Deck based on Joey and his "Red-Eyes B. Dragon", including "Red-Eyes Black Flare Dragon" and "Red-Eyes Archfiend of Lightning".
- 3 new Secret Rare cards: "Eternal Soul", "Dark Burning Attack", and "Dark Burning Magic".
- 3 Ultra Rare Token cards.

Each of the three decks include 3 Ultra Rares and 40 commons.
(Disclaimer: This sealed product features a 1996/2014 Copyright date.)

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value:
Each Legendary Decks II Collector's Set contains:

- 43-card Deck based on Yugi and his "Exodia the Forbidden One", including the 3 playable versions of the Egyptian God cards.
- 43-card Deck based on Kaiba and his "Blue-Eyes White Dragon".
- 43-card Deck based on Joey and his "Red-Eyes B. Dragon", including "Red-Eyes Black Flare Dragon" and "Red-Eyes Archfiend of Lightning".
- 3 new Secret Rare cards: "Eternal Soul", "Dark Burning Attack", and "Dark Burning Magic".
- 3 Ultra Rare Token cards.

Each of the three decks include 3 Ultra Rares and 40 commons.
